name: Planned vs Actual Therapy Session
query:
select
    name as "Therapy Plan:Link/Therapy Plan:220",
	total_sessions as "Planned Sessions:Int:150",
	total_sessions_completed as "Completed Sessions:Int:150",
	(total_sessions - total_sessions_completed) as "Variance:Int:100"
from `tabTherapy Plan`
where status!="Cancelled" and company=%(company)s
group by name
order by start_date desc
